  "title": "Management Trainee (F&B)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Work closely with the Manager.</li>\n  <li>Monitor outlet’s expenses, making sure that all costs are within the budget.</li>\n  <li>Assist manager to plan staff duty schedule for service crew and ensure sufficient staff and monthly management reports</li>\n  <li>Make every effort to let customers feel welcome with friendly and uncompromising service.</li>\n  <li>Supervise operations in outlet and serve customers.</li>\n  <li>Handle customer complaints, maintaining good customer relationships.</li>\n  <li>Progressively master the skills to run restaurant operations.</li>\n  <li>Receive training and perform duties in various sections of company’s operations.</li>\n  <li>Gain deep and thorough knowledge of the company’s restaurant operation by rotating on each position;</li>\n  <li>Solicit feedback from customers and staff, for areas of improvement and incorporate useful suggestions into operations.</li>\n  <li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned by superior.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor degree or above</li>\n  <li>Able to work on split shifts, weekends, and public holidays</li>\n  <li>Service oriented and passionate working in F&amp;B industry</li>\n  <li>Possess good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>PC literate, well-organized and self-motivated</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants please Whatsapp 9137 2746. Thank you</p>",
